    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for model risk level 3. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted given the standardized nature of the ASTM F1717 protocol and the conservative character of the single test configuration relative to in vivo loading. Overall credibility is assessed as Medium, consistent with the declared assurance level.",
